title: GOP sirens wail after Lamb claims win in PA
text:
GOP sirens wail after Lamb claims win in PA 5:40am EDT - 02:12 
Republicans sounded the alarm on Wednesday after Democrats claimed victory in a Pennsylvania congressional election seen as a referendum on U.S. President Donald Trump’s performance, although the vote tally remained officially too close to call. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
